Reasonable prices, lots of restriction and no ventilation. Shuttle service is a great +
So good

This Hotel complex is still the best short term and long term accommodation in the New Territory , the MTR is a short walk away, along with the Hotel bus, some services are free. Small cafe Bakery store on ground level as well as dry cleaner and a good gym and very large pool. Full groceries are round the corner at “Welcome “ and good shopping malls at the MTR. As well as a brilliant walking and biking tracks that go for kilometres and one of the prettiest parks in HK. What's not to like!
